title: Miss Venezuela 1995
text:
Miss Venezuela 1995 was the 42nd <a href="Miss%20Venezuela">Miss Venezuela</a> pageant, was held in <a href="Caracas">Caracas</a>, <a href="Venezuela">Venezuela</a> on September 27, 1995, after weeks of events. The winner of the pageant was <a href="Alicia%20Machado">Alicia Machado</a>, <a href="Yaracuy">Miss Yaracuy</a>.
The pageant was broadcast live on <a href="Venevisi%C3%B3n">Venevisión</a> from the <a href="Poliedro%20de%20Caracas">Poliedro de Caracas</a> in <a href="Caracas">Caracas</a>. At the conclusion of the final night of competition, outgoing titleholder <a href="Denyse%20Floreano">Denyse Floreano</a>, crowned <a href="Alicia%20Machado">Alicia Machado</a> of <a href="Yaracuy">Yaracuy</a> as the new <a href="Miss%20Venezuela">Miss Venezuela</a>.
